{"tid":1814923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退出? 乜重有得退咩?","createTime":"2020-01-07T06:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T13:53:33.000Z","uid":218313,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2668876e3563b3d27dd74aa4d68896d0804da16b","tid":1814923,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"呢幾一大堆勇武退出文<br />\n寫得呢D 文既我只諗到兩類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>1&gt; 狗/國安<br />\n2&gt; 悔氣撚<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n過左呢幾個月, 經歷左咁多事, 死左咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n乜仲有人覺得香港有得返轉頭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜仲有人覺得個運動可以隨隨便便就完?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪禁個Menu 出黎, 按一下logout 就回復正常?</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要呢個運動完, 得幾個可能:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">1&gt; 五大訴求 </span></strong><br />\n中共根本唔會俾你, 而且依家用緊一切方法消滅你抗爭既方法<br />\n所以中共一日存在, 我地係唔會得到我地要既野!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">2&gt; 中共解體</span></strong><br />\n之後香港自決去路<br />\n歸英/美好<br />\n聯邦好<br />\n獨立都好<br />\n香港人會走出一條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">3&gt; WWIII </span></strong><br />\nBOOM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該你地認清事實<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地係已經無路退</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n睇下新彊, 睇下維吾爾族<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港仲起緊個大監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廿三條黎緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">俾人抄左身份證既根本無得走</span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n評分系統會MARK 晒呢班人<br />\n香港人生生世世俾中共奴役<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">退? 退去邊?</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>幫推</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c83e781aba93b4de297dcfd036430aba0d0bbacf","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔<br />\n贏要靜靜雞<br />\n港獨要靜靜雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉風就大大聲<br />\nQuit game 都大大聲<br />\n互屌更加大大聲<br />\n都on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b4904a38e5385bc73697dfe7cbf95fada9aa1f9d","tid":1814923,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:58:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>退? 退去邊?</strong></span>"},{"pid":"45ea94ab91fc8c3ffdec9b74a712305870059c59","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c83e781aba93b4de297dcfd036430aba0d0bbacf","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔<br />\n贏要靜靜雞<br />\n港獨要靜靜雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉風就大大聲<br />\nQuit game 都大大聲<br />\n互屌更加大大聲<br />\n都on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"邊條7頭負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f27eeb032bc9db3810393077b8a6f56d6e3b62","tid":1814923,"uid":218313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45ea94ab91fc8c3ffdec9b74a712305870059c59","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c83e781aba93b4de297dcfd036430aba0d0bbacf","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔<br />\n贏要靜靜雞<br />\n港獨要靜靜雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉風就大大聲<br />\nQuit game 都大大聲<br />\n互屌更加大大聲<br />\n都on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"邊條7頭負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:00:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思, 係我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4085eac4aeb5fed5235e5173862577a6e3c65b1","tid":1814923,"uid":218313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"除非你有能力走<br />\n唔係, 退乜撚?"},{"pid":"491cf3a4619b7c4b163697b2af405ed51fecb163","tid":1814923,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"fc43891f5b58a79373a69e77c2a702043c61edd2","tid":1814923,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"根本睇一睇後面就係懸崖就唔會俾人帶風向<br />\n背水一戰 有前無後 不成功便成仁<br />\n而家帶風向想人退場果d係咩人 對邊一面最有利  自己諗"},{"pid":"1c0f29e0ef03cd5ab22df1d5e99a29d29f35e121","tid":1814923,"uid":212168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c83e781aba93b4de297dcfd036430aba0d0bbacf","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔<br />\n贏要靜靜雞<br />\n港獨要靜靜雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉風就大大聲<br />\nQuit game 都大大聲<br />\n互屌更加大大聲<br />\n都on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"帶風向 分化就梗係大大聲架啦  用下個腦<br />\n靜靜地點分化啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815ca78f5ed71b5d3e6b968b0a1847680d7a8bc4","tid":1814923,"uid":218313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc43891f5b58a79373a69e77c2a702043c61edd2","tid":1814923,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"根本睇一睇後面就係懸崖就唔會俾人帶風向<br />\n背水一戰 有前無後 不成功便成仁<br />\n而家帶風向想人退場果d係咩人 對邊一面最有利  自己諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:06:51.000Z","msg":"正解<br />\n以為仲有路退既, 根本就未認清依家個狀況有幾差<br />\n<br />\n勇武你估想做勇武?<br />\n有得揀, 邊個唔想享受?<br />\n<br />\n退? 退條毛"},{"pid":"d461fef4f07fa888a17613983463e26d6f9af741","tid":1814923,"uid":182365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:07:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"400f3f4af08c1d9d187265eebcc464c6bf0f76cf","tid":1814923,"uid":66099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"不割"},{"pid":"98b5765949cf826595d01a1764da1d28f92717bf","tid":1814923,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"好心寒，果堆postFB同連登有幾千正評<br />\n分化燃死全家"},{"pid":"d864cf6becf607ff5e8aa3fe1e28f4479eb40049","tid":1814923,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"仲有得返轉頭咩,可以退寺邊?"},{"pid":"b26e56b18273a7c7002afdb6e9ab334bb041b8b6","tid":1814923,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"退出入番一蚊又玩得ok?"},{"pid":"a95f04be7cb5b82f13ca4f99630e4ad770c71f15","tid":1814923,"uid":125670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:09:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4b106e2ebb59c51808513140ff43fb50ce0264ce","tid":1814923,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"無得退，永遠之戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7806318bd17ec2604bb69374de8c70e51a3673aa","tid":1814923,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d864cf6becf607ff5e8aa3fe1e28f4479eb40049","tid":1814923,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"仲有得返轉頭咩,可以退寺邊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:11:09.000Z","msg":"退到本能寺之變"},{"pid":"c31ac3b788ae5f7c3082d3217e03180c771b6f50","tid":1814923,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"試下用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「冇雙普選就獨立」</span></strong>做口號<br />\n<br />\n牌面上你係爭取緊無人有異議既雙普選。實質上你提供緊清晰既路徑，解釋緊點解要獨立、以及為獨立提供正當性。<br />\n<br />\n對於和理非，一開始可以則重係「雙普選」上面。但潛移默化地灌輸佢地獨立既可行性。對於獨派，亦解決左「時機」問題；因為嚴格上口號並唔係直接提倡獨立，但同時宣傳緊獨立。"},{"pid":"25a25ee626d9c9d3c6fff7f6cb87305d6cdaa158","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0f29e0ef03cd5ab22df1d5e99a29d29f35e121","tid":1814923,"uid":212168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c83e781aba93b4de297dcfd036430aba0d0bbacf","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔<br />\n贏要靜靜雞<br />\n港獨要靜靜雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉風就大大聲<br />\nQuit game 都大大聲<br />\n互屌更加大大聲<br />\n都on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"帶風向 分化就梗係大大聲架啦  用下個腦<br />\n靜靜地點分化啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"係阿 所以咪屌緊你班撚引戰打稻草人囉"},{"pid":"11e2d90d5b4dec2691d5b5b199cb6ae05b716951","tid":1814923,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"有得退, 就係即時落地獄 /牢獄, 極權者唔會放過任何異見人士"},{"pid":"26b39d027923357d2b1d3675a24541a8273500c8","tid":1814923,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a25ee626d9c9d3c6fff7f6cb87305d6cdaa158","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0f29e0ef03cd5ab22df1d5e99a29d29f35e121","tid":1814923,"uid":212168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c83e781aba93b4de297dcfd036430aba0d0bbacf","tid":1814923,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-lar